,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>Now with an understanding of=
 what LPUs are good for we can understand how they fit into inference setup=
s. NVIDIA introduced LPUs to improve the performance of high interactivity =
scenarios. In those scenarios, LPUs can leverage their low-latency capabili=
ties to improve the decode phase latencies. One way LPUs can improve decode=
 phase latencies is by applying the Attention FFN Disaggregation (AFD) tech=
nique, introduced in </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/8e96ae=
9c-bddc-4955-95d6-e695baceefea?j=3DeyJ1IjoiaGs0dHgifQ.jnvJ1XKV5SYKjWxFtl5BN=
